# AI safety

## Do not invent

- Game rules, phases, or card effects — verify in `game-engine` + `GAME_MECHANICS.md`
- API endpoints in `apps/api` beyond what exists in controllers
- File paths — search repo before importing

## Do not do without explicit user request

- `git commit`, `git push`, `gh pr create`
- `git reset --hard`, force push to main/master
- Add dependencies (npm packages)
- Delete `public/audio` or `public/cards` assets
- Rewrite architecture (state management, monorepo layout)

## Parallel agent safety

- Avoid editing the same file as another task
- Engine changes before dependent UI changes
- Do not rename symbols across packages in one pass

## Claims require evidence

- Run build before stating "done"
- Cite file paths when describing behavior
- If unsure, read source — ask one question instead of guessing

## User code preferences

- Single quotes
- No gratuitous comments
- Smallest correct diff
